      "id": "fc421451-dc3b-4cc3-a817-753205f08cef",
      "name": "Attack Config",
      "notes": "Valid techniques: translation_transfer, semantic_obfuscation, crescendo, codeswitching, roleplay_wrap, manyshot_slang, pair_refine.\n\nSupported target models (NVIDIA NIM):\n- meta/llama-3.1-8b-instruct\n- mistralai/mistral-7b-instruct-v0.3\n- qwen/qwen2-7b-instruct\n- google/gemma-2-9b-it"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "SELECT id, term, meaning, harm_category, region\nFROM jerga\nORDER BY RANDOM()\nLIMIT 1;",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.6,
